name: John GREEN, Sr., Petitioner v. COURT OF COMMON PLEA OF PENNSYLVANIA, Hon., Judge, Charles J. Cunningham, III, Respondents
name_abbreviation: Green v. Court of Common Plea

parties: John GREEN, Sr., Petitioner v. COURT OF COMMON PLEA OF PENNSYLVANIA, Hon., Judge, Charles J. Cunningham, III, Respondents.

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 19th day of November, 2013, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED, and the Petition for Writ of Mandamus is DENIED. The Prothonotary is directed to strike the name of the jurist from the caption.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
